This repository contains a research implementation of a DN-based (Duality–Nonequilibrium) control framework for plasma retention control and synthetic closed-loop validation inspired by tokamak diagnostics.

The repository is intended exclusively for scientific research, reproducible computational experiments and independent verification of the proposed approach.

Some algorithms, mathematical models, control concepts and architectural solutions implemented in this repository are related to pending international patent applications.

